"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1928151-British-athletes-2024-Olympics-boycott\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  British athletes are reportedly staging a boycott of theOlympicvillage's food in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 89, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998500744579487, \"rank\": 0.00014321361774624784, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 88, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.27995658619573e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB members are said to be refusing to eat in a number of restaurants because of supply shortages and being served uncooked meat.\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The food provisions have previously been hailed by organisers, who had vowed to provide quality food for competitors, supplied by Michelin star chefs.\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But instead chaos has reigned, with athletes subjected to lengthy queues and 'raw' chicken.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Team GB bosses are now set to fly in extra chefs from the UK to cook for the stars at their performance centre.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9552434777212574, \"rank\": 0.046827517874975876, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999989835203614, \"rank\": 1.011072915176558e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Anson, the British Olympic Association's chief executive, told theTimes:\\\"At the beginning of every Games there are usually two or three issues and the transportation is always one,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Anson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the big one this time is the food in the village, which is not adequate.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are not enough of certain foods: eggs, chicken, certain carbohydrates, and then there is the quality of the food, with raw meat being served to athletes.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have got to improve it over the next couple of days dramatically.\\\"\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Anson also explained how the discontent had forced team bosses to take action, with some stars even making their own packed lunches.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"score\": 0.9999999479514385, \"rank\": 5.203779642786111e-08, \"text\": \"Anson\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our athletes have decided they would rather go and eat in our performance lodge in Clichy, so we are having to get another chef to come over as the demand is far exceeding what we thought it would be,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1448, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clichy-sous-Bois\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.581239195477162e-22, \"text\": \"Clichy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clichy-sous-Bois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clichy-sous-Bois\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The athletes are not going there just to eat their lunch, they are packing meals for their dinner as they do not want to go into the athlete restaurant to eat.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are trying to make sure our athletes have an advantage by having more food.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the biggest issue at the moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Accomodation is spread across the suburbs of Saint-Denis, Saint Ouen and L'Ile-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accommodation_(religion)\", \"score\": 0.9294047605330832, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Accomodation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accommodation_(religion)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accommodation_(religion)\"}, {\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Ouen,_Jersey\", \"score\": 0.8773213638103508, \"rank\": 0.13983050847456185, \"text\": \"Saint Ouen\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Ouen,_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Ouen,_Jersey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 4,250 athletes are due to be housed during the Olympics, and 8,000 during the Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic chiefs have previously boasted that around 40,000 meals would be prepared every day in the village.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The largest restaurant venue, however, was said to have only 3,300 seats.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Elena Rybakina pulls out of Olympics just hours after draw was made  Do not miss:Man City decide Julian Alvarez price as striker 'wants to leave' after Olympics  Do not miss:Tennis star who collapsed at Wimbledon offers update after missing Olympics  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2249, \"end\": 2263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elena_Rybakina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elena Rybakina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elena_Rybakina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elena_Rybakina\"}, {\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2774372927304876e-13, \"text\": \"Man City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  A spokesman for Sodexo Live, the company in charge of catering, told L'Equipe the complaints were being taken \\\"very seriously.\\\"\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They said the complany was \\\"working to increase our supplies to the restaurants in the athletes' village.\\\"\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB has 327 athletes set to compete in Paris.\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9552434777212574, \"rank\": 0.046827517874975876, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.27995658619573e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http: